# Assets Directory

This directory contains runtime assets for the SDF Editor.

## Structure

- `shaders/` - WGSL shader files (if using external shaders)
- `textures/` - Texture resources
- `fonts/` - Font files for ImGui (optional)

## Notes

Currently, all shaders are embedded in the source code (SDFRenderer.cpp) for simplicity and cross-platform compatibility. This makes it easier to build for both native and web targets without worrying about file path resolution.

If you want to use external shader files instead, you can:
1. Place .wgsl files in the shaders/ directory
2. Modify the code to load them at runtime
3. Update the CMakeLists.txt to copy them to the build directory
